OL,3,CDangerous cyclists could face tougher
OL,4,Cprison sentences under new proposals
OL,6,FDangerous cyclists could face tougher
OL,7,Fsentences similar those enforced on ,
OL,8,Funder new proposals being debated in
OL,9,FParliament on Wednesday.
OL,11,FThe move would close a loophole which
OL,12,Fhas been campaigned against for years,
OL,13,Fthat only allows a to be jailed for a
OL,14,Fmaximum of two years for "wanton and
OL,15,Ffurious driving".
OL,17,FThe Victorian law introduced in 1861
OL,18,Fmeans cyclists aren't subject to the
OL,19,Fsame rules as car drivers, because the
OL,20,Fcurrent law only appplies to
OL,21,F"mechanically propelled" vehicles.
