OL,3,CDangerous cyclists could face tougher
OL,4,Cprison sentences under new proposals
OL,6,FMotorists can face a life sentence if
OL,7,Fthey're convicted of causing death by
OL,8,Fdangerous or reckless driving.
OL,10,FFormer leader of the Party Sir Iain
OL,11,FDuncan Smith has put forward a number
OL,12,Fof amendments to the Criminal Justice
OL,13,FBill being debated on Wednesday
OL,14,Fafternoon, which would mean people
OL,15,Friding bikes would face tougher
OL,16,Fpenalties if they injure of kill
OL,17,Fpedestrians.
